perceive: tells KB the current position and reachable neighbors; marks goal if reached.
reason: calls kb.infer() and queries for AtGoal.
act: calls perceive+reason, then moves greedily (Manhattan distance) toward goal.
agents/probabilistic_agent.py
update_beliefs: applies bayes_update to a single position using the sensor reading.
act: moves to the neighbor with the lowest obstacle probability in self.beliefs.
agents/hybrid_agent.py
perceive: adds KB facts about current position and low-belief (safe) neighbors.
plan: calls astar from the current position.
reason: runs kb.infer() and checks for goal.
update_beliefs: initializes the belief map then calls update_belief_map.
act: orchestrates all four in sequence and follows the first step of the planned path.
